<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="19" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
<bibRefCitation author="Martens, E von" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen Museum fuer Naturkunde Berlin, Zoologische Reihe" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" refId="B51" refString="Martens, E von, 1864. Ueber neue Mexikanische Landschnecken. Sitzsungsberichte der Gesellschaft fuer naturforschende Freunde zu Berlin (1863): 540-542." title="Ueber neue Mexikanische Landschnecken. Sitzsungsberichte der Gesellschaft fuer naturforschende Freunde zu Berlin (1863): 540 - 542." year="1864">Martens (1864)</bibRefCitation>
did not mention the number of specimens his description was based upon. The (subadult) specimen found in the ZMB collection does not confirm to the original measurements; it corresponds to the figure given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Martens, E von" journalOrPublisher="Conchologische Mittheilungen" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" refId="B59" refString="Martens, E von, 1890-1901. Land and freshwater Mollusca. In: Godman FD, Salvin O (eds.) Biologia Centrali-Americana: i-xxviii, 1-706. R.H. Poter and Dulau &amp; Co., London." title="Land and freshwater Mollusca. In: Godman FD, Salvin O (eds.) Biologia Centrali-Americana: i-xxviii, 1 - 706. R. H. Poter and Dulau &amp; Co., London." year="1890 - 1901">Martens (1893 [1890-1901])</bibRefCitation>
, but not to the figure given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Martens, E von" journalOrPublisher="Malakozoologische Blaetter" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" refId="B55" refString="Martens, E von, 1873. Die Binnenmollusken Venezuela's. Festschrift zur Feier des 100jaehrigen Bestehens der Gesellschaft fuer naturforschende Freunde zu Berlin: 157-225." title="Die Binnenmollusken Venezuela's. Festschrift zur Feier des 100 jaehrigen Bestehens der Gesellschaft fuer naturforschende Freunde zu Berlin: 157 - 225." year="1873">Martens (1873)</bibRefCitation>
. The current systematic position follows 
<bibRefCitation author="Thompson, FG" journalOrPublisher="Nachrichtsblatt der Deutschen Malakozoologischen Gesellschaft" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" refId="B109" refString="Thompson, FG, 2011. An annotated checklist and bibliography of the land and freshwater snails of Mexico and Central America. Bulletin Florida Museum of Natural History 50: 1-299." title="An annotated checklist and bibliography of the land and freshwater snails of Mexico and Central America. Bulletin Florida Museum of Natural History 50: 1 - 299." year="2011">Thompson (2011)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
